    path: /workspace/pf5-to-pf6-migration-checklist.md
    content: # PatternFly 5 тЖТ PatternFly 6: Comprehensive Migration Checklist

> **Source**: Official PatternFly upgrade guide (https://www.patternfly.org/get-started/upgrade/) and release notes, fetched 2025-05-30.

---

## Pre-requisites
- **Ensure PF5 upgrade is complete** тАФ Complete the PF5 upgrade process first (from https://v5-archive.patternfly.org/get-started/upgrade)
- **Codemods tool**: `npx @patternfly/pf-codemods@latest <path> --v6`
- **Run codemods BEFORE manual changes** тАФ running after will create more manual work

---

## 1. Package Changes

### Upgrade all @patternfly packages to v6
| Package | Action |
|---------|--------|
| `@patternfly/react-core` | Upgrade to v6 |
| `@patternfly/react-icons` | Upgrade to v6 |
| `@patternfly/react-tokens` | Upgrade to v6 |
| `@patternfly/react-charts` | Upgrade to v6 |
| `@patternfly/react-table` | Upgrade to v6 |
| `@patternfly/react-styles` | Upgrade to v6 |
| `@patternfly/react-component-groups` | Upgrade to v6 |
| `@patternfly/react-drag-drop` | New package for drag-and-drop (replaces DragDrop from react-core) |

### Victory Charts тАФ now optional peer dependency
- **Old**: Victory was bundled with `@patternfly/react-charts`
- **New**: Victory is an **optional peer dependency**. You must install it separately:
  - Install `victory` (covers all features), OR
  - Install specific packages like `victory-core`, `victory-tooltip`, etc.

### Deprecated package paths
| Old Import | New Import |
|------------|-----------|
| `@patternfly/react-core` (for deprecated components) | `@patternfly/react-core/deprecated` |
| `@patternfly/react-core/next` (for promoted components) | `@patternfly/react-core` |

### LogViewer stylesheet
- **Old**: LogViewer stylesheet was in the PatternFly package
- **New**: LogViewer stylesheet has moved to the LogViewer package itself тАФ may need to update stylesheet imports

---

## 2. Component API Changes (Props renamed/removed/changed)

### AccordionContent
- **Removed**: `isHidden` prop тАФ visibility now set automatically based on `isExpanded` on AccordionItem
- **Codemod**: Yes

### AccordionToggle
- **Moved**: `isExpanded` prop moved from AccordionToggle to AccordionItem
- **Old**: `<AccordionItem><AccordionToggle isExpanded /></AccordionItem>`
- **New**: `<AccordionItem isExpanded><AccordionToggle /></AccordionItem>`
- **Codemod**: Yes

### Avatar
- **Removed**: `border` prop
- **New**: Use `isBordered` prop instead
- **Old**: `<Avatar border={'dark'} />`
- **New**: `<Avatar isBordered />`
- **Codemod**: Yes

### Banner
- **Removed**: `variant` prop
- **New**: Use `color` or `status` props instead
- **Old**: `<Banner variant='red' />`
- **New**: `<Banner color='red' />`
- **Codemod**: Yes (replaces with `color`, may need manual review for `status`)

### Button
- **Renamed**: `isActive` тЖТ `isClicked`
- **Old**: `<Button isActive />`
- **New**: `<Button isClicked />`
- **Codemod**: Yes

- **Changed**: Icons must now be passed to the `icon` prop instead of as children (especially for `variant="plain"`)
- **Old**: `<Button variant="plain"><SomeIcon /></Button>`
- **New**: `<Button icon={<SomeIcon />} variant="plain" />`
- **Codemod**: Yes (for `variant="plain"` only)

- **Changed**: `isDisabled` now sets `disabled` attribute, no longer sets `aria-disabled` (except when `component` is not "button")
- **Changed**: Button text now wrapped in a `<div>` тАФ use `byRole` in tests instead of `byText`

### Card
- **Removed props**: `isSelectableRaised`, `isDisabledRaised`, `hasSelectableInput`, `selectableInputAriaLabel`, `onSelectableInputChange`, `isFlat`, `isRounded`
- **Changed**: For clickable-only cards, `selectableActions.selectableActionId` and `selectableActions.name` are no longer needed
- **Codemod**: Yes

### Checkbox / Radio
- **Replaced**: `isLabelBeforeButton` тЖТ `labelPosition="start"`
- **Old**: `<Checkbox isLabelBeforeButton />`
- **New**: `<Checkbox labelPosition="start" />`
- **Codemod**: Yes

### Color props (Banner, Label)
- **Renamed values**: `"cyan"` тЖТ `"teal"`, `"gold"` тЖТ `"yellow"`
- **Old**: `<Label color='gold' />` / `<Label color='cyan' />`
- **New**: `<Label color='yellow' />` / `<Label color='teal' />`
- **Codemod**: Yes

### DataListAction
- **Removed**: `isPlainButtonAction` prop
- **Codemod**: Yes

### Drawer
- **DrawerHead**: `hasNoPadding` prop removed
- **DrawerHead**: DrawerPanelBody no longer rendered internally тАФ use them independently
- **DrawerContent/DrawerPanelContent/DrawerSection**: `colorVariant="light-200"` тЖТ `colorVariant="secondary"`
- **DrawerContent**: `colorVariant="no-background"` removed; new `"primary"` value added
- **DrawerContent**: New `DrawerContentColorVariant` enum replaces `DrawerColorVariant` enum
- **Codemod**: Yes

### EmptyState
- **Major refactoring**: `EmptyStateHeader` and `EmptyStateIcon` no longer exported separately тАФ rendered internally within `EmptyState`
- **Old**: 
  ```jsx
  <EmptyState>
    <EmptyStateHeader titleText="Title" headingLevel="h4" icon={<EmptyStateIcon icon={CubesIcon} />} />
    <EmptyStateBody>Body</EmptyStateBody>
  </EmptyState>
  ```
- **New**:
  ```jsx
  <EmptyState titleText="Title" headingLevel="h4" icon={CubesIcon}>
    <EmptyStateBody>Body</EmptyStateBody>
  </EmptyState>
  ```
- **Props moved to EmptyState**: `titleText`, `headingLevel`, `icon`, `headerClassName`
- **Codemod**: Yes (but may require manual updates depending on implementation)

### ExpandableSection
- **Removed**: `isActive` prop
- **Codemod**: Mentioned in notable changes

### FormGroup
- **Renamed**: `labelIcon` тЖТ `labelHelp`
- **Old**: `<FormGroup labelIcon={<>Help</>} />`
- **New**: `<FormGroup labelHelp={<>Help</>} />`
- **Codemod**: Yes

### FormFieldGroupHeaderTitleTextObject (interface)
- **Fixed typo**: `FormFiledGroupHeaderTitleTextObject` тЖТ `FormFieldGroupHeaderTitleTextObject`
- **Codemod**: Yes

### HelperTextItem
- **Removed props**: `hasIcon`, `isDynamic`
- Icon now renders automatically when `variant` is not "default" or when `icon` prop is passed
- `screenReaderText` now renders only when `variant` is not "default"
- **Codemod**: Yes

### JumpLinksItem
- **Required prop**: `href` is now required
- **Changed**: Uses Button component internally; `onClick` type changed to `React.MouseEvent` (from `React.MouseEvent<HTMLAnchorElement>`)

### Label
- **Replaced**: `isOverflowLabel` тЖТ `variant="overflow"`
- **Old**: `<Label isOverflowLabel />`
- **New**: `<Label variant="overflow" />`
- **Codemod**: Yes

### LoginMainFooterLinksItem
- **Restructured**: Props like `href`, `linkComponentProps` removed; everything now passed as children
- **Old**: `<LoginMainFooterLinksItem href="..." linkComponentProps={...}><i>Icon</i></LoginMainFooterLinksItem>`
- **New**: `<LoginMainFooterLinksItem><Button variant="link" component="a" href="...">...</Button></LoginMainFooterLinksItem>`
- **Codemod**: Yes

### Masthead
- **Removed**: `backgroundColor` prop (theming no longer React-side)
- **Renamed**: `MastheadBrand` тЖТ `MastheadLogo`
- **New component**: `MastheadBrand` (new wrapper around `MastheadLogo`)
- **Structure change**: `MastheadToggle` and `MastheadBrand` must now be wrapped in `MastheadMain`
- **Old**:
  ```jsx
  <Masthead>
    <MastheadToggle>Toggle</MastheadToggle>
    <MastheadMain><MastheadBrand>Logo</MastheadBrand></MastheadMain>
  </Masthead>
  ```
- **New**:
  ```jsx
  <Masthead>
    <MastheadMain>
      <MastheadToggle>Toggle</MastheadToggle>
      <MastheadBrand><MastheadLogo>Logo</MastheadLogo></MastheadBrand>
    </MastheadMain>
  </Masthead>
  ```
- **Codemod**: Yes

### MenuToggle
- **Changed**: Icons should be passed to `icon` prop instead of as children (especially for `variant="plain"`)
- **Old**: `<MenuToggle variant='plain'><EllipsisVIcon /></MenuToggle>`
- **New**: `<MenuToggle icon={EllipsisVIcon} variant='plain' />`
- **Codemod**: Yes

### Nav
- **Renamed variant**: `"tertiary"` тЖТ `"horizontal-subnav"`
- **Old**: `<Nav variant="tertiary" />`
- **New**: `<Nav variant="horizontal-subnav" />`
- **Removed**: `theme` prop (use light/dark mode theming instead)
- **Codemod**: Yes

### NavItem
- **Removed**: `hasNavLinkWrapper` prop
- **New**: Icons should be passed to new `icon` prop
- **Codemod**: Yes

### Page
- **Renamed props**:
  - `header` тЖТ `masthead`
  - `isTertiaryNavGrouped` тЖТ `isHorizontalSubnavGrouped`
  - `isTertiaryNavWidthLimited` тЖТ `isHorizontalSubnavWidthLimited`
  - `tertiaryNav` тЖТ `horizontalSubnav`
- **Codemod**: Yes

### PageBreadcrumb / PageSection
- **New prop**: `hasBodyWrapper` (defaults to `true`)
- `isWidthLimited` no longer determines whether children are wrapped in PageBody
- **PageSection `variant` prop**: Now only accepts `"default"` or `"secondary"` (values like `"dark"` removed)
- **Removed**: `PageSectionTypes.nav` type value
- **Removed component**: `PageNavigation` тАФ removed entirely, use `PageSection` instead
- **Codemod**: Yes

### PageHeaderToolsItem
- **Removed**: `isSelected` prop
- **Codemod**: Yes

### PageSidebar
- **Removed**: `theme` prop (theming no longer React-side)
- **Codemod**: Yes

### Popper / Dropdown / Select
- **Changed default**: `appendTo` now defaults to `document.body` (previously varied)

### SimpleFileUpload
- **Removed**: `aria-describedby` from internal TextInput; `id` from browse button
- **New prop**: `browseButtonAriaDescribedby`
- **Recommendation**: Use `FileUploadHelperText` component as child instead of `FormHelperText`

### Switch
- **Removed**: `labelOff` prop
- **Codemod**: Yes

### Tabs
- **Renamed**: `isSecondary` тЖТ `isSubtab`
- **Old**: `<Tabs isSecondary />`
- **New**: `<Tabs isSubtab />`
- **Renamed variant value**: `"light300"` тЖТ `"secondary"`
- **Old**: `<Tabs variant='light300' />`
- **New**: `<Tabs variant="secondary" />`
- **Codemod**: Yes

### Toolbar
- **Removed props**:
  - `Toolbar`: `usePageInsets`
  - `ToolbarContent`: `alignSelf`
  - `ToolbarItem`: `widths`
  - `ToolbarToggleGroup`: `alignment`
- **Renamed ChipтЖТLabel props** (across multiple Toolbar sub-components):
  - `customChipGroupContent` тЖТ `customLabelGroupContent`
  - `chipContainerRef` тЖТ `labelContainerRef`
  - `chips` тЖТ `labels`
  - `deleteChipGroup` тЖТ `deleteLabelGroup`
  - `deleteChip` тЖТ `deleteLabel`
  - `chipGroupExpandedText` тЖТ `labelGroupExpandedText`
  - `chipGroupCollapsedText` тЖТ `labelGroupCollapsedText`
  - `expandableChipContainerRef` тЖТ `expandableLabelContainerRef`
  - `chipGroupContentRef` тЖТ `labelGroupContentRef`
- **Renamed interfaces**:
  - `ToolbarChipGroupContentProps` тЖТ `ToolbarLabelGroupContentProps`
  - `ToolbarChipGroup` тЖТ `ToolbarLabelGroup`
  - `ToolbarChip` тЖТ `ToolbarLabel`
- **Renamed component**: `ToolbarChipGroupContent` тЖТ `ToolbarLabelGroupContent`
- **Replaced props**:
  - `spacer` тЖТ use `gap`, `columnGap`, or `rowGap` instead
  - `spaceItems` тЖТ removed from ToolbarGroup and ToolbarToggleGroup
  - `spacer` values map: `spacerNone` тЖТ `gapNone`, `spacerSm` тЖТ `gapSm`, `spacerMd` тЖТ `gapMd`, etc.
- **Renamed align values**: `"alignLeft"` тЖТ `"alignStart"`, `"alignRight"` тЖТ `"alignEnd"`
- **ToolbarGroup/ToolbarToggleGroup variant renames**:
  - `"button-group"` тЖТ `"action-group"`
  - `"icon-button-group"` тЖТ `"action-group-plain"`
- **ToolbarItem variant changes**:
  - `"chip-group"` тЖТ `"label-group"`
  - `"bulk-select"`, `"overflow-menu"`, `"search-filter"` тЖТ removed
- **Codemod**: Yes

### WizardStep
- **Changed**: `body` prop no longer accepts `null`
- **Old**: `<WizardStep body={null} />`
- **New**: `<WizardStep />`
- **Codemod**: Yes

---

## 3. Component Removals / Replacements

| Removed Component | Replacement | Notes |
|-------------------|-------------|-------|
| **Chip** | **Label** (with `variant="outline"`, `onClose` replaces `onClick`) | Deprecated тЖТ `@patternfly/react-core/deprecated`; or replace with Label |
| **ChipGroup** | **LabelGroup** | Same as above |
| **Tile** | **Card** (see new Card-as-Tile example in docs) | Deprecated тЖТ `@patternfly/react-core/deprecated` |
| **Text / TextContent / TextList / TextListItem** | **Content** (single component) | See detailed mapping below |
| **PageNavigation** | Removed entirely | Use `PageSection` instead |
| **KebabToggle** | **MenuToggle** with `variant="plain"` and `icon={<EllipsisVIcon />}` | |
| **DragDrop / Droppable / Draggable** | **DragDropSort** from `@patternfly/react-drag-drop` | Deprecated тЖТ `@patternfly/react-core/deprecated` |
| **DualListSelector** (old) | **DualListSelector** (new, promoted from `/next`) | Old тЖТ `@patternfly/react-core/deprecated` |
| **Modal** (old) | **Modal** (new, promoted from `/next`) | Old тЖТ `@patternfly/react-core/deprecated` |
| **Application Launcher** (deprecated) | Custom menu implementation | Removed from deprecated |
| **Context Selector** (deprecated) | Custom menu implementation | Removed from deprecated |
| **Dropdown** (deprecated, old) | Current composable Dropdown or Dropdown template | Removed from deprecated |
| **Options Menu** (deprecated) | Current composable Select or Select template | Removed from deprecated |
| **Page Header** (deprecated) | Masthead + Toolbar | Removed from deprecated |
| **Select** (deprecated, old) | Current composable Select or Select template | Removed from deprecated |

### Text тЖТ Content detailed mapping
| Old | New |
|-----|-----|
| `<Text>` | `<Content component="p">` |
| `<Text component="h3">` | `<Content component="h3">` |
| `<TextContent>` | `<Content>` |
| `<TextContent isVisited>` | `<Content isVisitedLink>` |
| `<TextList>` | `<Content component="ul">` |
| `<TextList component="ol">` | `<Content component="ol">` |
| `<TextList isPlain>` | `<Content component="ul" isPlainList>` |
| `<TextListItem>` | `<Content component="li">` |
| `<TextListItem component="dt">` | `<Content component="dt">` |
| `TextVariants` | `ContentVariants` |
| `TextListVariants` | `ContentVariants` |
| `TextListItemVariants` | `ContentVariants` |
| `TextProps` | `ContentProps` |

---

## 4. Import Path Changes

### Charts тАФ Victory imports moved to subdirectory
- **Old**: `import { Chart } from '@patternfly/react-charts';`
- **New**: `import { Chart } from '@patternfly/react-charts/victory';`
- Applies to ALL Victory-based chart components

### Deprecated components moved to `/deprecated`
- **Old**: `import { Chip } from '@patternfly/react-core';`
- **New**: `import { Chip } from '@patternfly/react-core/deprecated';`
- Same for: DragDrop, Droppable, Draggable, DualListSelector (old), Modal (old), Tile

### Promoted components moved from `/next` to main
- **Old**: `import { Modal } from '@patternfly/react-core/next';`
- **New**: `import { Modal } from '@patternfly/react-core';`
- Same for: DualListSelector (new)

### React tokens тАФ prefix changed
- **Old**: `import global_FontSize_lg from '@patternfly/react-tokens/dist/esm/global_FontSize_lg';`
- **New**: `import t_global_font_size_lg from '@patternfly/react-tokens/dist/esm/t_global_font_size_lg';`
- Token names now prefixed with `t_` when their value is a PF token variable (with `--pf-t` prefix)

### react-component-groups renames
| Old Import | New Import |
|------------|-----------|
| `ContentHeader` | `PageHeader` |
| `InvalidObject` | `MissingPage` |
| `NotAuthorized` | `UnauthorizedAccess` |

---

## 5. CSS / Token Changes

### CSS class prefix change
- **Old**: `pf-v5-*` (e.g., `pf-v5-c-button`)
- **New**: `pf-v6-*` (e.g., `pf-v6-c-button`)
- **Codemod**: `class-name-updater` with `--v6` flag

### CSS variable system overhaul тАФ design tokens
- **Old**: `--pf-v5-global--FontSize--lg`
- **New**: `--pf-t--global--font--size--lg`
- All `--pf-v5-*` variables replaced with `--pf-t--*` token variables
- **Removed variables list**: https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/e/2PACX-1vQqeH7ThYi0jkhYEB8B2SXa7x8AaY5T9ajG6o-Ogz3p7YVp0OuTulb_L3DYLDrHlY4zUE3IBiup6tkN/pubhtml?gid=1160160856&single=true
- **Added variables list**: https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/e/2PACX-1vQqeH7ThYi0jkhYEB8B2SXa7x8AaY5T9ajG6o-Ogz3p7YVp0OuTulb_L3DYLDrHlY4zUE3IBiup6tkN/pubhtml?gid=268831450&single=true

### Global color tokens тАФ NO auto-fix available
- Color tokens replaced with temporary hot-pink placeholder `--pf-t--temp--dev--tbd` (or `t_temp_dev_tbd` in React)
- These **MUST be manually replaced** with appropriate PF6 color tokens
- Example: `--pf-v5-global--Color--100` тЖТ manually find replacement in PF6 token docs

### React token name format change
- **Old format**: `global_FontSize_lg`, `global_Color_100`
- **New format**: `t_global_font_size_lg`, `t_global_color_nonstatus_green_clicked`
- Not all have 1:1 mappings

### Component/chart tokens
- Component-level and chart tokens need **manual replacement** тАФ no auto-fix
- Example: `c_badge_PaddingLeft`, `c_alert__FontSize` тАФ no codemod fix

### CSS logical direction changes
- `--pf-v6-c-slider__step--Left` тЖТ `--pf-v6-c-slider__step--InsetInlineStart`
- `--pf-v6-c-table__sticky-cell--Left` тЖТ `--pf-v6-c-table__sticky-cell--InsetInlineStart`
- `--pf-v6-c-table__sticky-cell--Right` тЖТ `--pf-v6-c-table__sticky-cell--InsetInlineEnd`

### Three codemods for CSS/tokens
1. **class-name-updater**: `npx @patternfly/class-name-updater <path> --v6 --fix` тАФ renames `pf-v5` тЖТ `pf-v6` classes
2. **tokens-update** (part of pf-codemods): Updates global CSS vars in React/.js/.tsx files
3. **css-vars-updater**: Updates CSS vars in .css, .scss, .md files

---

## 6. Theming Changes

- **Theme props removed across components** тАФ theming is no longer handled React-side:
  - `Masthead`: `backgroundColor` prop removed
  - `Nav`: `theme` prop removed
  - `PageSidebar`: `theme` prop removed
  - `Avatar`: `border` prop removed (use `isBordered` instead)
- **Use CSS light/dark mode theming** instead of React props
- **Design token system**: PF6 introduces a new design token system (`--pf-t--*` prefix) replacing old `--pf-v5-global--*` variables
- **All existing CSS overrides targeting PF5 variables will break** тАФ must be removed or updated
- **`colorVariant` changes**:
  - `"light-200"` тЖТ `"secondary"` (Drawer, PageSection)
  - `"no-background"` тЖТ removed (DrawerContent)
  - `"light300"` тЖТ `"secondary"` (Tabs)
  - `PageSection variant` now only accepts `"default"` or `"secondary"`

---

## 7. Icons Changes

- **Icons for Button**: Must be passed to `icon` prop, not as children
  - `<Button variant="plain"><Icon /></Button>` тЖТ `<Button variant="plain" icon={<Icon />} />`
- **Icons for MenuToggle**: Must be passed to `icon` prop
  - `<MenuToggle variant="plain"><EllipsisVIcon /></MenuToggle>` тЖТ `<MenuToggle variant="plain" icon={EllipsisVIcon} />`
- **Icons for NavItem**: New `icon` prop for passing icons
- **KebabToggle replacement**: Use `<MenuToggle variant="plain" icon={<EllipsisVIcon aria-hidden="true" />} />`
- **Import paths unchanged** for `@patternfly/react-icons` (but version must be bumped to v6)

---

## 8. Charts Changes

### Import path change (CRITICAL)
- **Old**: `import { Chart, ChartArea, ... } from '@patternfly/react-charts';`
- **New**: `import { Chart, ChartArea, ... } from '@patternfly/react-charts/victory';`
- ALL Victory-based chart imports must add `/victory` subpath

### Victory as optional peer dependency
- Victory is no longer bundled тАФ install separately:
  - `npm install victory` (for all features)
  - OR install specific packages: `victory-core`, `victory-tooltip`, etc.

### Future chart libraries
- The `/victory` directory structure allows future chart libraries to be added without including Victory dependencies

---

## 9. Layout Changes

### Toolbar spacer/spacing changes
- `spacer` prop тЖТ replaced with `gap`, `columnGap`, `rowGap`
- `spaceItems` prop тЖТ removed
- Values renamed: `spacerNone` тЖТ `gapNone`, `spacerSm` тЖТ `gapSm`, etc.

### Toolbar alignment changes
- `"alignLeft"` тЖТ `"alignStart"`
- `"alignRight"` тЖТ `"alignEnd"`

### Breakpoints now use rem units (not pixels)
| Breakpoint | Token | Old (px) | New (rem) |
|------------|-------|----------|-----------|
| xs | `--pf-t--global--breakpoint--xs` | 0px | 0rem |
| sm | `--pf-t--global--breakpoint--sm` | 576px | 36rem |
| md | `--pf-t--global--breakpoint--md` | 768px | 48rem |
| lg | `--pf-t--global--breakpoint--lg` | 992px | 62rem |
| xl | `--pf-t--global--breakpoint--xl` | 1200px | 75rem |
| 2xl | `--pf-t--global--breakpoint--2xl` | 1450px | 90.625rem |

- Any pixel-based breakpoint logic must be updated to use rem values

---

## 10. Form Changes

### FormGroup
- `labelIcon` тЖТ `labelHelp`
- Recommend using `FormGroupLabelHelp` element
- Markup wraps labelHelp in `<span className="pf-v6-c-form__group-label-help">`

### Checkbox / Radio
- `isLabelBeforeButton` тЖТ `labelPosition="start"`

### FormFieldGroupHeaderTitleTextObject
- Typo fixed: `FormFiledGroupHeaderTitleTextObject` тЖТ `FormFieldGroupHeaderTitleTextObject`

### HelperTextItem
- `hasIcon` and `isDynamic` removed
- Icon auto-renders when `variant` is not "default"
- `screenReaderText` only renders when `variant` is not "default"

### SimpleFileUpload
- `aria-describedby` removed from internal TextInput
- `id` removed from browse button
- New: `browseButtonAriaDescribedby` prop
- Use `FileUploadHelperText` instead of `FormHelperText`

---

## 11. Navigation Changes

### Nav
- `variant="tertiary"` тЖТ `variant="horizontal-subnav"`
- `theme` prop removed

### NavItem
- `hasNavLinkWrapper` prop removed
- New `icon` prop for icons

### Page navigation props renamed
- `header` тЖТ `masthead`
- `tertiaryNav` тЖТ `horizontalSubnav`
- `isTertiaryNavGrouped` тЖТ `isHorizontalSubnavGrouped`
- `isTertiaryNavWidthLimited` тЖТ `isHorizontalSubnavWidthLimited`

### PageNavigation
- Component **removed entirely**

### Tabs
- `isSecondary` тЖТ `isSubtab`
- `variant="light300"` тЖТ `variant="secondary"`
- Scroll buttons markup updated (now use Button components, wrapped in div)

---

## 12. Modal / Wizard Changes

### Modal
- **Old Modal deprecated** тЖТ moved to `@patternfly/react-core/deprecated`
- **New Modal promoted** from `@patternfly/react-core/next` тЖТ `@patternfly/react-core`
- **Old**: `import { Modal } from '@patternfly/react-core/next';`
- **New**: `import { Modal } from '@patternfly/react-core';`
- **Codemod**: Yes

### Wizard
- **WizardStep**: `body` prop no longer accepts `null`
- **WizardFooter**: Now uses ActionList around Button components
- **WizardNavItem**: Wrapper element `pf-v6-c-wizard__nav-link-main` added; error icon renders before content
- **WizardToggle**: Now renders error icon for error status

---

## 13. Other Breaking Changes

### Accordion markup
- AccordionItem now renders a `div` wrapper element

### Button test changes
- `aria-disabled` no longer rendered when `false` or when `component="button"`
- Button text wrapped in `<div>` тАФ use `byRole` instead of `byText` in tests

### Select test changes
- RTL queries may not find menu options after selection (Popper set to `aria-disabled`)
- Fix: Pass `{hidden: true}` option or change `appendTo` to `inline`

### Data-codemods cleanup
- After all codemods run, run `--only data-codemods-cleanup` to remove `data-codemods` attributes/comments

### LoginMainHeader markup
- Uses `div` wrapper instead of `header` element

### NotificationBadge markup
- Uses stateful button internally

### NotificationDrawerHeader
- No longer uses Text component internally; renders native `h1`

### Pagination markup
- Wrapper element around PaginationOptionsMenu toggle

### MenuItemAction markup
- Uses Button internally; wrapper around action button; no icon wrapper inside

### TreeView
- `pf-m-selectable` class removed from list items тАФ update selectors, tests, snapshots

### SliderStep
- `--pf-v6-c-slider__step--Left` тЖТ `--pf-v6-c-slider__step--InsetInlineStart`

### Duplicate imports cleanup
- Codemod removes duplicate import specifiers

### Unused imports cleanup
- Codemod removes unused PatternFly imports

### react-component-groups renames
| Old Component | New Component |
|---------------|---------------|
| `ContentHeader` | `PageHeader` |
| `InvalidObject` | `MissingPage` |
| `NotAuthorized` | `UnauthorizedAccess` |

### react-component-groups prop renames
| Component | Old Prop | New Prop |
|-----------|----------|----------|
| ErrorState | `errorTitle` | `titleText` |
| ErrorState | `errorDescription` | `bodyText` |
| ErrorState | `defaultErrorDescription` | `defaultBodyText` |
| InvalidObject (MissingPage) | `invalidObjectTitleText` | `titleText` |
| InvalidObject (MissingPage) | `invalidObjectBodyText` | `bodyText` |
| NotAuthorized (UnauthorizedAccess) | `description` | `bodyText` |
| NotAuthorized (UnauthorizedAccess) | `title` | `titleText` |
| UnavailableContent | `unavailableTitleText` | `titleText` |
| UnavailableContent | `unavailableBodyPreStatusLinkText` + `unavailableBodyPostStatusLinkText` | `bodyText` (combined) |
| LogSnippet | `leftBorderVariant` | `variant` |
| LogSnippet | `LogSnippetBorderVariant` enum | Use PF `AlertVariant` enum values as strings |
| MultiContentCard | `leftBorderVariant` | Removed |
| MultiContentCard | `withHeaderBorder` | Removed |

---

## Migration Steps Summary

1. **Update all `@patternfly/*` package versions** to v6
2. **Install Victory** separately if using charts: `npm install victory`
3. **Run codemods**: `npx @patternfly/pf-codemods@latest <path> --v6` (inspect first, then `--fix`)
4. **Run class-name-updater**: `npx @patternfly/class-name-updater <path> --v6 --fix`
5. **Run tokens-update**: Part of pf-codemods тАФ updates React tokens and CSS vars in JS/TSX
6. **Run css-vars-updater**: Updates CSS vars in .css/.scss/.md files
7. **Manually replace hot-pink placeholder tokens** (`t_temp_dev_tbd` / `--pf-t--temp--dev--tbd`) with correct color tokens
8. **Remove or update all CSS overrides** targeting old PF5 variables
9. **Update pixel-based breakpoint logic** to rem values
10. **Run data-codemods-cleanup**: `npx @patternfly/pf-codemods@latest <path> --v6 --only data-codemods-cleanup`
11. **Build, test, and visually review** your application
12. **Update tests**: Fix `byText` тЖТ `byRole` for buttons, update snapshot tests for class name changes, etc.



