    <h4>Verdict</h4>
    <p><code>pf-codemods</code> made <strong>zero</strong> package.json changes тАФ this is the fundamental flaw of this branch. It applied codemods that transform source code to PF6 API patterns but left the actual packages at v5, causing every transformation to produce a type error. This is the <em>opposite</em> of the official guidance, which says to upgrade packages first.</p>
    <p><code>semver/goose</code> upgraded all 10 PF packages, added the new <code>react-drag-drop</code> package, installed Victory chart dependencies, and also upgraded supporting packages (React 18, OpenShift SDK). This is a complete package migration.</p>
