<!-- 6.5 React 18 Compatibility -->
<details id="react-compat">
  <summary>тЪЫя╕П React 18 Compatibility &nbsp;<span class="badge badge-green">semver/goose wins</span></summary>
  <div class="details-content">
    <h4>Why React 18 matters for PF6</h4>
    <p>PatternFly 6 requires React 18+. This means the React upgrade is not "scope creep" тАФ it is a <strong>prerequisite</strong> for PF6. Key React 18 changes include: removal of <code>React.SFC</code>, <code>children</code> prop no longer implicit in <code>React.FC</code>, <code>act()</code> returns a Promise, and various type changes.</p>

